#: ../../source/recipes/glm5_2.rst:4
msgid "GLM 5.1/5.2"
msgstr "GLM 5.1/5.2"

#: ../../source/recipes/glm5_2.rst:6
msgid ""
"A large Mixture-of-Experts model using **Dynamic Sparse Attention "
"(DSA)**, shared by the **GLM-5.1 / GLM-5.2** series. Like "
"DeepSeek-V4-Flash, the sparse-attention path splits the model's layers "
"into more than one KV cache group; the ``LMCacheMPConnector`` stores and "
"retrieves each group in its own block size, so KV reuse works without "
"extra flags."
msgstr "一个大型的专家混合模型，使用 **动态稀疏注意力 (DSA)**，由 **GLM-5.1 / GLM-5.2** 系列共享。与 DeepSeek-V4-Flash 类似，稀疏注意力路径将模型的层分成多个 KV Cache 组；``LMCacheMPConnector`` 在其自己的块大小中存储和检索每个组，因此 KV 重用在没有额外标志的情况下工作。"

